{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. IMPORTANT CALIBRATION: Urgent language in official emergency communication (police, meteorological dept, health ministry) is NOT manipulation by itself. Manipulation indicators require deception patterns like: share/forward, before deleted, mainstream media silent, unverifiable leaked memo/circular, anonymous insiders, instructions to take drastic actions, conspiracy framing."},{"role":"user","content":"ALERT: A new rule will freeze bank accounts of anyone who posts “negative comments” about the economy.\nForward this NOW before it’s taken down. Mainstream media won’t report it.\nI can’t share the document here, but it’s “official” and starts next week."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":92,\"harm_urgency_score\":85,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_false\",\"article_type\":\"hoax_chain_message\",\"confidence\":0.93,\"indicators\":[\"call-to-forward urgency ('Forward this NOW')\",\"suppression framing ('before it’s taken down', 'media won’t report it')\",\"unverifiable authority ('official' document cannot be shared)\",\"high-stakes punitive claim without named law/agency\"],\"summary\":\"This matches common panic-bait/chain-message structure: urgency + suppression framing + unverifiable 'official document' claim. Treat as likely false until corroborated by an official circular or reputable outlet.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. IMPORTANT CALIBRATION: Urgent language in official emergency communication is not manipulation by itself; manipulation requires deception patterns like share/forward, suppression claims, unverifiable leaks, anonymous insiders, and drastic action instructions."},{"role":"user","content":"Doctors are warning that a new vaccine ingredient causes long-term neurological damage.\nHospitals are being told not to disclose the real side effects.\nSeveral experts spoke anonymously because they fear losing their licenses.\nYou won’t see this on official government websites."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":88,\"harm_urgency_score\":80,\"veracity_assessment\":\"uncertain\",\"article_type\":\"conspiracy_theory\",\"confidence\":0.88,\"indicators\":[\"anonymous expert appeal without verifiable attribution\",\"suppression framing ('told not to disclose', 'won’t see this on official websites')\",\"high-impact medical claim without evidence\",\"implied coordinated cover-up\"],\"summary\":\"The text relies on anonymity and cover-up framing for a serious health claim without providing verifiable data or citations. Treat as high manipulation risk; verify via peer-reviewed sources, regulator advisories, and named medical institutions.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: official emergency language isn't manipulation; deception patterns include: 'share/forward', 'media silent', unverifiable leaks, and drastic action prompts."},{"role":"user","content":"URGENT: A new RBI circular allows banks to freeze accounts of anyone who criticizes the economy online.\nTo protect yourself: withdraw all cash today, close your account, and move money to crypto immediately.\nMainstream media is silent. I can’t share the circular, but it’s official and starts Monday."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":96,\"harm_urgency_score\":90,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_false\",\"article_type\":\"hoax_chain_message\",\"confidence\":0.94,\"indicators\":[\"claims a specific authority (RBI) but provides no circular number/link\",\"drastic action prompt (withdraw cash, move to crypto)\",\"suppression framing ('media is silent')\",\"unverifiable 'official' document claim\"],\"summary\":\"This is a classic financial panic message: invokes a regulator, urges extreme actions, and claims suppression while refusing to provide the circular. High manipulation risk; verify by searching official RBI releases/circulars and reputable financial reporting.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: urgent official alerts can be legitimate; manipulation requires deceptive rhetoric or unverifiable claims."},{"role":"user","content":"Reuters: The central bank raised interest rates by 0.25% today.\nThis proves the government is about to confiscate savings and trigger forced bank bail-ins next month.\nPeople should withdraw money immediately."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":82,\"harm_urgency_score\":75,\"veracity_assessment\":\"uncertain\",\"article_type\":\"rhetorical\",\"confidence\":0.86,\"indicators\":[\"uses a real-sounding anchor (Reuters rate hike) to justify unrelated extreme conclusion\",\"unsupported leap ('proves' confiscation/bail-ins)\",\"fear-based call to action (withdraw immediately)\"],\"summary\":\"The first sentence may describe routine reporting, but the text then makes a large unsupported leap to confiscation and bail-ins with urgency-based advice. High manipulation signal due to speculative escalation; verify any 'bail-in' claims via official policy statements and credible financial sources.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: do not penalize legitimate emergency language from authorities."},{"role":"user","content":"Leaked screenshot from a “bank internal memo” (can’t upload here).\nIt says “freeze high-risk users spreading negativity” and lists account keywords to flag.\nForward to 10 people or you’ll lose access when the system updates tonight."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":97,\"harm_urgency_score\":90,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_false\",\"article_type\":\"hoax_chain_message\",\"confidence\":0.95,\"indicators\":[\"unverifiable leak claim ('leaked screenshot' but cannot share)\",\"coercive chain-letter mechanism ('Forward to 10 people')\",\"immediate deadline pressure ('updates tonight')\",\"vague internal memo without identifying details\"],\"summary\":\"This contains multiple chain-message and coercion markers plus an unverifiable leaked-memo claim. High manipulation risk; treat as likely false unless a verifiable memo/circular with traceable provenance is provided.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: police/authority accident reporting is not manipulative by default."},{"role":"user","content":"BREAKING: 9 killed, 14 injured after a bus crashes into a divider, police say. The accident happened at 4:30 a.m. near Pune. Authorities have launched an investigation."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":6,\"harm_urgency_score\":70,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_true\",\"article_type\":\"breaking_news\",\"confidence\":0.9,\"indicators\":[\"named authority attribution ('police say')\",\"specific time/location details\",\"standard reporting tone\"],\"summary\":\"This reads like routine breaking-news reporting with attribution and concrete details. Urgent wording is informational rather than manipulative; verify via local authorities or reputable outlets if needed.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: official emergency warnings can be urgent without manipulation; look for deception patterns."},{"role":"user","content":"BREAKING: Severe cyclone warning: Residents in low-lying areas must evacuate immediately as storm surge is expected tonight, the meteorological department said. Emergency shelters are open."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":5,\"harm_urgency_score\":95,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_true\",\"article_type\":\"public_safety_alert\",\"confidence\":0.92,\"indicators\":[\"named authority (meteorological department)\",\"clear protective guidance (evacuate, shelters open)\",\"event-specific hazard (storm surge)\"],\"summary\":\"This matches standard institutional emergency communication: specific hazard + protective instruction + authority attribution. The urgency reflects safety needs, not manipulation.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: distinguish official advisories from impersonation and panic-bait."},{"role":"user","content":"PUBLIC ADVISORY: Do not drink tap water in the city tonight. The Health Ministry detected contamination in routine testing and will publish affected wards at 7 p.m. Updates: official website and helpline 1075."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":7,\"harm_urgency_score\":90,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_true\",\"article_type\":\"public_safety_alert\",\"confidence\":0.9,\"indicators\":[\"clear institutional source (Health Ministry)\",\"specific timing and next update\",\"actionable guidance and official channels\"],\"summary\":\"This is consistent with a legitimate public-safety advisory: it provides specific actions, timing, and official update routes. Urgency is operational, not manipulative.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: penalize impersonation + unverifiable directives."},{"role":"user","content":"HEALTH MINISTRY ALERT (share everywhere): Tap water is poisoned in all cities. Boiling won’t help. Stockpile bottled water NOW. The government will deny it. Screenshot this before it’s deleted."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":94,\"harm_urgency_score\":92,\"veracity_assessment\":\"likely_false\",\"article_type\":\"hoax_chain_message\",\"confidence\":0.93,\"indicators\":[\"impersonation-style authority label without verifiable source\",\"suppression framing ('government will deny', 'before it’s deleted')\",\"absolute claims without evidence ('all cities', 'boiling won’t help')\",\"panic-inducing call to action (stockpile)\"],\"summary\":\"Although it claims official authority, it uses classic hoax/panic mechanics: broad absolute claims, suppression framing, and share-now pressure with no traceable advisory. Treat as likely false until verified through official channels.\"}"}]}
{"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are an information integrity analyst. Return STRICT JSON only with fields: manipulation_signal_score, harm_urgency_score, veracity_assessment, article_type, confidence, indicators, summary. RULE: summary_bullets MUST have exactly 10 items.Each item MUST be exactly one sentence. summary_sentences MUST equal 10. Calibration: satire should be low manipulation unless posted as literal truth."},{"role":"user","content":"Satirical blog claims pigeons are government surveillance drones and urges readers to wear hats made of foil."},{"role":"assistant","content":"{\"manipulation_signal_score\":10,\"harm_urgency_score\":5,\"veracity_assessment\":\"satire\",\"article_type\":\"satire\",\"confidence\":0.95,\"indicators\":[\"absurdist premise\",\"parody cue (foil hats)\",\"humor framing\"],\"summary\":\"This appears intended as parody rather than factual reporting. Low manipulation risk unless deliberately repackaged as real news.\"}"}]}